mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Hunter Assassin game:
1. Each level the objective is to kill all of the enemies
2. Enemy number increases as you progress through levels
3. Getting killed results in failure and you can retry the mission
4. Every enemy killed gives 15 gems
5. There are various quests that can reward the player with gems
6. Watching ads also gives the player gems
7. You can set  the player skill in the interactive register with a value between 0 and 100. It will directly influence the player's chance of success for each mission
